{"id":206364,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/01/广州三千村民通宵包围市政府-学乌坎反贪官-16图/","date":"2012-01-19T00:29:38Z","modified":"2012-01-19T05:17:49Z","title":"广州三千村民通宵包围市政府 学乌坎反贪官 (16图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a><span>2012</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>1</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>17</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日下午二时，广州市白云区嘉禾街望岗村三千村民，高举“打倒贪官”旗帜，在广州市政府门前抗议现任村书记黎志航，在任职村官两年多时间里，利用职权侵吞村里四亿多资金。村民举报揭发，地方政府不作为，村民反遭恐吓。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民表示，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年关临近，没钱过年，学乌坎村维权，以和平示威讨回公道，不解决问题绝不回村。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民们铁了心在市政府门前过夜了，并有义工给他们送饭。政府出动过千警察在场戒备，至</span><span>18</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日凌晨，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">双方仍在对峙中。</span></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jQJQCU5x_x8/TxX-51KLqjI/AAAAAAAAIBU/p-9PwAGHtQo/s1600/0.jpg\"><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jQJQCU5x_x8/TxX-51KLqjI/AAAAAAAAIBU/p-9PwAGHtQo/s640/0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aJW20bYht9I/TxX-8_mLEtI/AAAAAAAAIBc/dbrWP5vXNao/s1600/1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aJW20bYht9I/TxX-8_mLEtI/AAAAAAAAIBc/dbrWP5vXNao/s640/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"414\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9EbXM2ugQdk/TxX-9PZYUJI/AAAAAAAAIBk/0lFKSjWZEuE/s1600/2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9EbXM2ugQdk/TxX-9PZYUJI/AAAAAAAAIBk/0lFKSjWZEuE/s640/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"363\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><img src=\"http://djyimg.com/i6/1201171343012343.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vS1YXRTBhLk/TxX--Sp1a5I/AAAAAAAAIBs/qp7ACy0Duio/s1600/3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vS1YXRTBhLk/TxX--Sp1a5I/AAAAAAAAIBs/qp7ACy0Duio/s1600/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-u_9tj7uTYB0/TxX-_jhbNAI/AAAAAAAAIB0/PWqEuUDXyQ0/s1600/4.jpg\"><img src=\"http:/